Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=The Descent Into Hell
  - 220
By: William Law
---
What we are to feel and undergo in these last purifications, when the
deepest root of all selfishness, as well spiritual as natural, is to
be plucked up and torn from us, or how we shall be able to stand in
that trial, are both of them equally impossible to be known by us
beforehand.
